      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3"
      ],
      "start": 19.16,
      "text": "Competition in frontier AI is accelerating across coding, voice, and video. Moonshot AI has released Kimi K2.7 Code, an open-source model built for agentic coding tasks."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "adef89dd539",
        "a6e7f1fa2e2"
